WEBVTT

00:00:03.660 --> 00:00:13.660
David was faithful to Jehovah for decades, but then he led his guard down, and he coveted

00:00:13.660 --> 00:00:23.329
a married woman.

00:00:23.329 --> 00:00:28.539
Bring Veshiba to me.

00:00:28.539 --> 00:00:38.179
David and Veshiba committed adultery, and she became pregnant.

00:00:38.179 --> 00:00:54.490
To hide their sin, David secretly ordered Veshiba's husband to be killed, and he hurt

00:00:54.490 --> 00:00:57.969
the God who had done so much for him.
